# /etc/apparmor.d/local/usr.bin.lsfs — Local AppArmor profile augmentation for LSFS
# This file is read by the abstraction and can be used to add LSFS-specific rules
#
# LSFS (LLM-based Semantic File System) runs searches using natural language
# against local vector DB. The profile restricts:
#  - File system access to allowed directories
#  - Network access to localhost only (Qdrant gRPC)
#  - No ability to execute arbitrary code
